C A data file for diablo.  This is a generic, easy method of data
C input, as long as you don't change the number of comment lines.
C Note that the grid size is defined in the file grid_def.
C  FLAVOR  FLAVORS FLAVORI VERSION  Linear,Lineart,Bick,Gyre,Gyr2,Turb,Beta,NFlo/FKPP,NPZ,chmo,diff,NPZ2,BSTA/HD,PR
   'Linear'  'diff'   'PR'    1.0        
C   USE_MPI      USE_LES   (note, also change these flags in Makefile):
    .TRUE.       .FALSE.               
C Parameters:         NU,          LX,    LY,    LZ  With Bick/Gyr2, change x,z coord
                     1D-3          3      1     3
C Method:     NUM_PER_DIR, CREATE_NEW_FLOW
                  3            .FALSE.        
C Time March:  N_TIME_STEPS, DELTA_T, RESET_TIME, VARIABLE_DT, CFL, UPDATE_DT
                 1000        0.002     .FALSE.     .FALSE.    0.5      1
C I/O:         VERBOSITY, SAVE_FLOW_INT, SAVE_STATS_INT,  MOVIE
                   2           10          100000       .FALSE. 
C Here include 6*N_TH lines, see below for format
C         CREATE_FLOW_TH(1)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
C         FILTER_TH(1)         FILTER_INT(1)     (If and how often to filter)
             .TRUE.                 10 
C         RI_TAU(1)      PR(1)       REACTION(1)
             0.0         1D0           0.0
C         CREATE_FLOW_TH(2)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
C         FILTER_TH(2)         FILTER_INT(2)     (If and how often to filter)
               .TRUE.                10
C         RI_TAU(2)      PR(2)       REACTION(2)
             0.0         1D0       0.
C         CREATE_FLOW_TH(3)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
C         FILTER_TH(3)         FILTER_INT(3)     (If and how often to filter)
               .TRUE.                10
C         RI_TAU(3)      PR(3)       REACTION(3)
             0.0         1D0        0.


C When including scalar advection, include 6 lines like the following for each scalar

C         CREATE_FLOW_TH(1)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
C         FILTER_TH(1)         FILTER_INT(1)     (If and how often to filter)
               .TRUE.                10
C         RI_TAU(1)      PR(1)       BACKGROUND_TH(N)
             0.0             1.0          .FALSE.

